Tick (dt):
    Fix timestep at kt:
        pre-physics hook (kt)
            Calculation of intentions and forces
                AI
                Computations based on controller state
        physics tick (kt)
            Collision handlers
        post-physics hook (kt)
            Checking results
                Hit points

Display update:
    Pre-display hook:
        Copy positions and rotations
            With offscreen culling for efficiency using an AABB physics query
        Update UI elements
    Buffer flip
    (Post-display hook is not useful)

    
